    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just being quiet though. it's like the story's already ended and i'm just... stuck in the epilogue. i look at my hands and i don't see a creator anymore, just someone waiting for time to pass. doesn't it feel like once the meaning is gone, everything else is just a burden?",
